    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I recently read Jeni&#39;s book and loved it as well.  I made the sweet corn ice cream (without the blackberry sauce) and I added a little more corn to the initial mixture.  It was like eating the best ear of corn ever!!!  I then used her basic recipe to make blueberry basil ice cream and it is really heaven in a bowl.  </p>
<p>The first time I made the ice cream I also felt like I used a lot of bowls, but the second time it seemed much easier and faster.  It was certainly much easier and faster than the custard style I have usually made.</p>
