    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Earlier this summer I saw a recipe for Jeni&#39;s Sweet Corn &#038; Black Raspberry Ice Cream, but I passed it by. All the odd ingredients were such a turn-off. Now that I have a better understanding of why I need corn syrup and cream cheese, maybe I should give it a try! I just hope corn and raspberries are still in season.</p>
