    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>The corn syrup poster has it a little wrong &#8211;corn syrup can&#39;t &#8220;contain&#8221; HFCS as High-fructose corn syrup is, by definition, a variant of corn syrup. </p>
<p>That being said, corn syrup not great for you either, just has less badness than HFCS. </p>
<p>Personally, I would try a mild flavored honey if you are worried about corn syrup.</p>
    </div>

      </li><!-- #comment-## -->
