    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I used to live in Ohio and have visited Jeni&#39;s place in the Short North in Columbus several times &#8211; it&#39;s so scrumptious and I haven&#39;t been able to find anything close it it here in Michigan.  Thanks for posting the recipe (and noting that she now has a cookbook)!  We can&#39;t wait to try this one out &#8211; it&#39;s sure to bring back great memories.</p>
